 		UNAME_RELEASE=`/usr/sbin/sizer -v | awk '{print $3}'`

 	sed 's/^	//' << EOF >$dummy.c

 	&& OS_REL=.`sed -n 's/[^ ]* [^ ]* \([0-9][0-9]\).*/\1/p' < /etc/.relid`
